OL,6,FA hospital emergency care unit has
OL,7,Fbeen graded as 'inadequate' by the
OL,8,Fhealth watchdog.
OL,10,FThe Countess of Chester Hospital was
OL,11,Fissued with an urgent warning notice
OL,12,Fafter 'repeated breaches' were found
OL,13,Fin legal regulations in five areas by
OL,14,Fthe Care Quality Commission (CQC).
OL,16,FThe inspection, carried out in
OL,17,FFebruary 2025, found there were
OL,18,Fnumerous breaches in a variety of
OL,19,Fareas, including dignity and respect -
OL,20,Fand safeguarding from abuse.
