OL,3,CEmergency department rated
OL,4,C'inadequate' by health watchdog
OL,6,FThe inspection came in response to
OL,7,Fconcerns around access, flow, and care
OL,8,Fof both mental health patients in the
OL,9,Fdepartment, and patients in non-
OL,10,Fclinical areas.
OL,12,FThe CQC has now issued a warning
OL,13,Fnotice to the trust, saying it must
OL,14,Fmake significant improvements to their
OL,15,Fquality of healthcare.
OL,17,FThe notice breaches five of the legal
OL,18,Fregulations in relation to: dignity
OL,19,Fand respect, safeguarding from abuse
OL,20,Fand improper treatment, premises and
OL,21,Fequipment, governance and staffing.
