OL,6,FOfficers also raised concerns about
OL,7,Finfection prevention describing
OL,8,Fequipment in some areas as "visibly
OL,9,Fdirty".
OL,11,FHealthwatch highlighted concerns about
OL,12,Flong waiting times, lack of privacy,
OL,13,Fand inconsistent communication.
OL,15,FHowever, the service demonstrated a
OL,16,Fstrong commitment to learning,
OL,17,Fimprovement, and staff wellbeing.
