OL,6,FJane Tomkinson, Chief Executive
OL,7,FOfficer of the Countess of Chester
OL,8,FHospital was "disappointed by the
OL,9,Frecent rating."
OL,11,FShe said: "Whilst we have seen
OL,12,Fimprovements, it is clear the actions
OL,13,Ftaken in the last 12 months need to be
OL,14,Fenhanced to consistently deliver the
OL,15,Fexperience and care our patients
OL,16,Fdeserve.
