OL,6,F"During the inspection and on receipt
OL,7,Fof the warning notice we took
OL,8,Fimmediate action. Our focus remains on
OL,9,Faddressing some long-standing
OL,10,Fchallenges and we are committed to
OL,11,Fsupporting our teams to ensure that
OL,12,Fthe actions we take lead to
OL,13,Fsustainable improvements in our
OL,14,Fservices.
OL,16,F"We will continue to work closely with
OL,17,Four regulators and we anticipate a
OL,18,Ffurther inspection in due course where
OL,19,Fthe improvements will be demonstrated."
